Linda Mtula and his co-accused Leeroy Morrison are accused of killing the young mother and dumping her body on a field in Athlone. CAPE TOWN - The boyfriend of murdered 26-year-old Aviwe Jam Jam has appeared briefly in the Athlone Magistrates Court. Linda Mtula and his co-accused Leeroy Morrison are accused of killing the young mother and dumping her body on a field in Athlone in July. She was beaten to death. The case has been postponed to 3 October for a bail application.